987
00:39:01,510 --> 00:39:03,470
- No way.
 -  You don't have to apologise.

988
00:39:03,470 --> 00:39:05,310
- We should apologise.
 -  You can beat me.

989
00:39:05,310 --> 00:39:07,540
He said, "I'll never draw such a cartoon."

990
00:39:07,540 --> 00:39:09,170
It's more embarrassing if you go home.

991
00:39:09,170 --> 00:39:12,500
- I'm sure you can beat me.
