999
00:39:27,850 --> 00:39:29,780
- Let go of his hands.
 -  Come on.

1000
00:39:30,580 --> 00:39:31,880
Be careful.

1001
00:39:32,820 --> 00:39:34,870
(Seok Jin grabs Jo Seok's name tag.)

1002
00:39:34,870 --> 00:39:36,990
(I'm winning unintentionally.)

1003
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:39,320
- His arms are too short.
 -  This is too harsh.

1004
00:39:39,850 --> 00:39:41,010
He won!

1005
00:39:41,010 --> 00:39:42,440
He's being too harsh.

1006
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,250
(Jo Seok ripped off Seok Jin's name tag.)

1007
00:39:46,720 --> 00:39:48,640
- He won!
 -  He won!

1008
00:39:48,640 --> 00:39:50,410
(Jo Seok won.)

1009
00:39:50,410 --> 00:39:53,070
- He won!
 -  Let's toss him into the air.

1010
00:39:53,070 --> 00:39:54,150
- In 3, 2, 1.
 -  In 3, 2, 1.

1011
00:39:54,490 --> 00:39:55,520
(It's Jo Seok first win.)

1012
00:39:55,990 --> 00:39:57,570
- In 3, 2, 1.
 -  He was strong.

1013
00:39:57,570 --> 00:39:59,510
- He was so strong.
 -  You did a great job.

1014
00:39:59,510 --> 00:40:01,140
He was strong.

1015
00:40:01,140 --> 00:40:04,070
- You're the best.
 -  Seok Jin almost won.

1016
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:06,270
- Seok Jin was trying to win.
 -  He was.

1017
00:40:06,270 --> 00:40:08,940
- Seok Jin lost. – He's really strong.

1018
00:40:08,940 --> 00:40:10,910
Jo Seok is finally smiling.

1019
00:40:10,910 --> 00:40:12,570
- You won!
 -  You did a great job.

1020
00:40:12,570 --> 00:40:14,730
If you didn't win, you wouldn't have been able to sleep tonight.

1021
00:40:14,730 --> 00:40:17,070
Jo Seok will draw us.

1022
00:40:17,070 --> 00:40:19,570
- Really?
 -  That'll be amazing.

1023
00:40:19,570 --> 00:40:21,610
- Give us your autograph, too.
 -  Your autograph.

1024
00:40:21,610 --> 00:40:23,930
- Who is he drawing?
 -  I think it's Kwang Soo.

1025
00:40:23,930 --> 00:40:25,320
It's obviously Kwang Soo.

1026
00:40:25,750 --> 00:40:27,920
- It looks like Kwang Soo.
 -  It does.

1027
00:40:28,490 --> 00:40:31,340
Do you draw the webtoons yourself?

1028
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:32,980
He does.

1029
00:40:32,980 --> 00:40:35,350
He's so tall.

1030
00:40:35,990 --> 00:40:37,840
- It's that body.
 -  I recognise this body.

1031
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,440
- It's the body from his webtoon.
 -  It's a rubber body.

1032
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:40,610
I'm not that tall.

1033
00:40:40,610 --> 00:40:41,940
It's exactly like his webtoon.

1034
00:40:41,940 --> 00:40:43,580
Are you angry at me?

1035
00:40:44,550 --> 00:40:45,990
(Smiling)

1036
00:40:46,620 --> 00:40:49,050
- That's amazing.
 -  Thank you.

1037
00:40:49,050 --> 00:40:50,340
- Pose like the drawing.
 -  Okay.

1038
00:40:50,340 --> 00:40:51,710
- Thank you.
 -  It does look like him.

1039
00:40:51,710 --> 00:40:53,780
Who would you like to draw next?

1040
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:56,220
It's Gary.

1041
00:40:56,220 --> 00:40:58,520
- It's Gary.
 -  Is it Jo Seok?

1042
00:40:58,880 --> 00:41:00,170
Isn't it Jo Seok?

1043
00:41:00,170 --> 00:41:01,910
- I think it's Jong Kook.
 -  No, it's Gary.

1044
00:41:01,910 --> 00:41:03,270
- Is it Jong Kook?
 -  It's Gary.

1045
00:41:03,270 --> 00:41:05,640
- It's Jong Kook.
 -  It's obviously you.

1046
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:08,140
- Look at the hair.
 -  It is Jong Kook.

1047
00:41:08,140 --> 00:41:10,540
It's you. Look at the eyes.

1048
00:41:10,540 --> 00:41:12,140
- It's me.
 -  The neck is the same.

1049
00:41:12,140 --> 00:41:13,540
- It's the same.
 -  It's really me.

1050
00:41:13,540 --> 00:41:15,800
- It looks exactly like you.
 -  It's definitely me.

1051
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:17,340
It's definitely Jong Kook.

1052
00:41:17,340 --> 00:41:19,020
(A satisfied fan)

1053
00:41:19,420 --> 00:41:23,170
