1054
00:41:23,170 --> 00:41:27,160
- Jo Seok, we'd like to apologise.
 -  Right.

1055
00:41:27,160 --> 00:41:28,470
We'll give you a golden name tag.

1056
00:41:28,470 --> 00:41:30,270
It's a golden name tag.

1057
00:41:30,270 --> 00:41:33,410
We'd like to give you a golden name tag.

1058
00:41:33,410 --> 00:41:34,780
Thank you.

1059
00:41:35,580 --> 00:41:38,460
Will you accept our apology?

1060
00:41:38,460 --> 00:41:41,050
I wasn't sure if I should come today.

1061
00:41:42,150 --> 00:41:44,910
Now, I think it was a good idea.

1062
00:41:44,910 --> 00:41:46,500
- It was nice today, wasn't it?
 -  Yes, it was.

1063
00:41:46,500 --> 00:41:50,410
I'll put this on my studio wall.

1064
00:41:50,410 --> 00:41:53,370
- Thank you.
 -  We'll put this on our walls, too.

1065
00:41:53,370 --> 00:41:57,160
- Since he accepted our apology,
 -  Right.

1066
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:59,140
- let's give him a big hand.
 -  Okay.

1067
00:41:59,140 --> 00:42:01,170
- Thank you.
 -  Thank you.

1068
00:42:01,170 --> 00:42:03,650
- Thank you.
 -  We'll look forward to your work.

1069
00:42:05,080 --> 00:42:07,950
(We were sorry.)

1070
00:42:08,620 --> 00:42:12,150
(They're on their way to meet the next person.)

1071
00:42:13,050 --> 00:42:15,140
Don't you feel sorry to Kyuhyun as well?

1072
00:42:15,140 --> 00:42:17,070
- I do.
 -  That episode in particular.

1073
00:42:17,070 --> 00:42:19,010
I feel sorry to everyone in that episode,

1074
00:42:19,010 --> 00:42:20,770
- including Yenny.
 -  Everyone.

1075
00:42:20,770 --> 00:42:22,340
- I feel sorry to everyone.
 -  Rap Monster.

1076
00:42:22,340 --> 00:42:24,010
- Rap Monster, too.
 -  And John Park.

1077
00:42:24,010 --> 00:42:25,340
I feel so sorry to Kyuhyun.

1078
00:42:25,340 --> 00:42:27,440
Does anyone have his phone number? Why don't we call him?

1079
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:29,620
- I have his number.
 -  Let's try it.

1080
00:42:30,950 --> 00:42:37,310
(They're calling Kyuhyun.)

1081
00:42:37,310 --> 00:42:38,620
- Hello?
 -  Kyuhyun.

1082
00:42:40,250 --> 00:42:41,980
- Hello?
 -  Hi.

1083
00:42:41,980 --> 00:42:43,470
- It's me.
 -  He sounds cold.

1084
00:42:43,470 --> 00:42:45,710
- He's cold.
 -  Kyuhyun, I'm sorry.

1085
00:42:45,710 --> 00:42:46,880
He must really be upset.

1086
00:42:47,450 --> 00:42:49,650
It's the first time you've called me.

1087
00:42:50,220 --> 00:42:51,840
(Jae Seok is embarrassed.)

1088
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:53,990
That's why I'm sorry. Where are you?

1089
00:42:54,520 --> 00:42:56,910
I'm in Japan right now.

1090
00:42:56,910 --> 00:42:58,270
Are you in Japan?

1091
00:42:58,270 --> 00:42:59,710
- Japan?
 -  Yes.

1092
00:42:59,710 --> 00:43:02,940
I've apologised to you...

1093
00:43:02,940 --> 00:43:04,810
many times.

1094
00:43:04,810 --> 00:43:07,340
- Have you really?
 -  Hey.

1095
00:43:07,340 --> 00:43:09,140
- He must be really angry.
 -  I did.

1096
00:43:09,140 --> 00:43:11,840
- Yes, I have.
 -  Apologise to him.

1097
00:43:11,840 --> 00:43:14,110
I want to apologise. It's Gary.

1098
00:43:14,110 --> 00:43:15,980
Gary...

1099
00:43:15,980 --> 00:43:19,170
was the one who initiated it.

1100
00:43:19,170 --> 00:43:20,910
- Gary is sorry.
 -  Right.

1101
00:43:20,910 --> 00:43:24,510
So Gary, can you go to Fukuoka?

1102
00:43:24,510 --> 00:43:25,940
- Me?
 -  You should go.

1103
00:43:25,940 --> 00:43:27,280
Kyuhyun.

1104
00:43:27,650 --> 00:43:29,610
- Yes.
 -  Then...

1105
00:43:29,610 --> 00:43:31,240
- Gary, you should go.
 -  I'll...

1106
00:43:31,240 --> 00:43:33,110
- You should go.
 -  meet you in Fukuoka...

1107
00:43:33,110 --> 00:43:34,720
and apologise.

1108
00:43:35,550 --> 00:43:36,810
(Really?)

1109
00:43:36,810 --> 00:43:39,050
I finally arrived in Fukuoka.

1110
00:43:39,050 --> 00:43:41,940
(Gary is in Japan.)

1111
00:43:41,940 --> 00:43:43,720
I'm here to meet Kyuhyun.

1112
00:43:43,720 --> 00:43:48,390
(Let's find Kyuhyun in Fukuoka.)

1113
00:43:48,390 --> 00:43:50,940
So many of his fans are here.

1114
00:43:50,940 --> 00:43:52,430
(Kyuhyun, please accept our apology.)

1115
00:43:52,430 --> 00:43:55,970
- In 1, 2, 3.
 -  Go, Kyuhyun!

1116
00:43:55,970 --> 00:43:57,570
- Go, Kyuhyun!
 -  Go, Kyuhyun!

1117
00:43:57,570 --> 00:43:59,570
It's here. Kyuhyun!

1118
00:43:59,570 --> 00:44:01,310
(Will Kyuhyun accept our apology?)

1119
00:44:01,310 --> 00:44:04,250
(The global Apology Service is coming soon.)

1120
00:44:05,420 --> 00:44:08,040
(Who's the fourth person to receive an apology?)

1121
00:44:08,040 --> 00:44:10,470
- I hope Hee Jun will show up...
 -  Right.

1122
00:44:10,470 --> 00:44:12,240
chubbier than before.

1123
00:44:12,240 --> 00:44:13,410
- Wait.
 -  Really.

1124
00:44:13,410 --> 00:44:16,040
It's all your fault.

1125
00:44:16,040 --> 00:44:17,770
It was your personal mistake.

1126
00:44:17,770 --> 00:44:20,640
- We don't have to apologise.
 -  You laughed, too.

1127
00:44:20,640 --> 00:44:24,040
We laughed but he might have been hurt.

1128
00:44:24,040 --> 00:44:26,310
I remember that day.

1129
00:44:26,310 --> 00:44:30,070
We had to go into the water a lot.

1130
00:44:30,070 --> 00:44:31,320
(Let's review what happened.)

1131
00:44:32,280 --> 00:44:34,410
Get down, you fatty.

1132
00:44:34,410 --> 00:44:36,340
You should give it to me.

1133
00:44:36,340 --> 00:44:39,410
(Fatty)

1134
00:44:39,410 --> 00:44:40,520
Fatty?

1135
00:44:40,920 --> 00:44:43,520
My mum is watching this.

1136
00:44:45,020 --> 00:44:48,240
No one could have called him fatty during his H.O.T. days.

1137
00:44:48,240 --> 00:44:51,060
- Really.
 -  If it was back then,

1138
00:44:51,060 --> 00:44:52,940
Jong Kook wouldn't be living in this country.

1139
00:44:52,940 --> 00:44:55,610
His fans would cut out my eyes in my pictures.

1140
00:44:55,610 --> 00:44:56,940
You'd be killed.

1141
00:44:56,940 --> 00:44:58,340
He's coming.

1142
00:44:58,340 --> 00:45:00,340
- He wouldn't be here.
 -  He's coming.

1143
00:45:00,340 --> 00:45:02,650
(He's finally here.)

1144
00:45:03,020 --> 00:45:07,820
(A chubby figure approaches.)

1145
00:45:09,180 --> 00:45:10,920
(Moon Hee Jun)

1146
00:45:11,350 --> 00:45:13,640
- He's here.
 -  Hello.

1147
00:45:13,640 --> 00:45:14,810
You're even chubbier now.

1148
00:45:14,810 --> 00:45:18,170
I won't sit down until Jong Kook leaves.

1149
00:45:18,170 --> 00:45:19,570
Hee Jun, come here.

1150
00:45:19,570 --> 00:45:21,340
- Hee Jun.
 -  Jong Kook should leave first.

1151
00:45:21,340 --> 00:45:23,220
It's been a long time.

1152
00:45:23,620 --> 00:45:25,070
Hee Jun.

1153
00:45:25,070 --> 00:45:26,270
- We're sorry.
 -  Hee Jun.

1154
00:45:26,270 --> 00:45:28,340
One of the members of H.O.T. is here.

1155
00:45:28,340 --> 00:45:29,980
- Where have you been?
 -  Stop that.

1156
00:45:32,380 --> 00:45:35,070
Has that incident...

1157
00:45:35,070 --> 00:45:37,470
- caused you any trouble?
 -  Be honest.

1158
00:45:37,470 --> 00:45:38,640
- Since that incident.
 -  Did you have a hard time?

1159
00:45:38,640 --> 00:45:40,240
- Has it caused me trouble?
 -  Yes.

1160
00:45:40,240 --> 00:45:41,570
(Did I have a hard time?)

1161
00:45:41,570 --> 00:45:44,070
- When I search my name...
 -  Why?

1162
00:45:44,070 --> 00:45:45,310
- What happens?
 -  What?

1163
00:45:45,310 --> 00:45:47,570
Does the word "Fatty" show up when you search your name?

1164
00:45:47,570 --> 00:45:49,970
"Moon Hee Jun Fatty", "Fatty Moon Hee Jun"...

1165
00:45:49,970 --> 00:45:51,640
and "Fatty". All three of them show up.

1166
00:45:51,640 --> 00:45:53,540
It drives me crazy.

1167
00:45:53,540 --> 00:45:55,910
If it was only one, I could do something about it.

1168
00:45:55,910 --> 00:45:57,570
But all the different word combinations show up.

1169
00:45:57,570 --> 00:45:59,580
One in the Western way and one in the Korean way.

1170
00:45:59,920 --> 00:46:01,610
"Moon Hee Jun Fatty", "Fatty Moon Hee Jun"...

1171
00:46:01,610 --> 00:46:02,640
- and "Fatty".
 -  "Fatty".

1172
00:46:02,640 --> 00:46:05,750
I searched for "Fatty" and all I find are pictures of you.

1173
00:46:07,080 --> 00:46:09,650
- Read it.
 -  "To the legendary idol, Hee Jun."

1174
00:46:09,980 --> 00:46:14,140
"We're sorry we upset you by calling you "Fatty" and "Yoyo"."

1175
00:46:14,140 --> 00:46:18,810
"We're also sorry for upsetting your mother as well."

1176
00:46:18,810 --> 00:46:20,220
We're sorry.

1177
00:46:20,650 --> 00:46:22,240
You should apologise to his mother first.

1178
00:46:22,240 --> 00:46:24,270
My mother was really hurt.

1179
00:46:24,270 --> 00:46:26,340
- She was?
 -  Was she really?

1180
00:46:26,340 --> 00:46:28,570
She has been texting me every day since then.

1181
00:46:28,570 --> 00:46:29,740
- Does she tell you to lose weight?
 -  Yes.

1182
00:46:29,740 --> 00:46:32,840
I'm sure she wanted to say that to you anyway.

1183
00:46:32,840 --> 00:46:35,640
Jong Kook. I have never heard my mother...

1184
00:46:35,640 --> 00:46:36,850
swear in my life.

1185
00:46:37,550 --> 00:46:39,220
But she said, "Is that jerk out of his mind?"

1186
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:41,220
Really.

1187
00:46:41,620 --> 00:46:43,310
Just because you have a fit body...

1188
00:46:43,310 --> 00:46:45,770
- She was sad that I was hurt.
 -  I didn't mean it.

1189
00:46:45,770 --> 00:46:49,910
It was just my cute way of calling you.

1190
00:46:49,910 --> 00:46:52,340
- Why don't we give her a call?
 -  Are you calling my mother?

1191
00:46:52,340 --> 00:46:54,940
- Jong Kook must apologise.
 -  Are they really calling my mum?

1192
00:46:54,940 --> 00:46:56,750
(He'll apologise to Hee Jun's mother over the phone.)

1193
00:46:57,880 --> 00:46:59,340
- Mum.
 -  Yes?

1194
00:46:59,340 --> 00:47:00,480
It's me.

1195
00:47:01,280 --> 00:47:02,380
So?

1196
00:47:02,880 --> 00:47:04,770
She doesn't care.

1197
00:47:04,770 --> 00:47:06,570
- Do you remember?
 -  She's not in a good mood.

1198
00:47:06,570 --> 00:47:09,280
- What?
 -  When I was on Running Man,

1199
00:47:10,180 --> 00:47:12,710
- Right.
 -  Jong Kook called me a fatty,

1200
00:47:12,710 --> 00:47:15,310
- so you got mad, right?
 -  Of course!

1201
00:47:15,310 --> 00:47:16,810
- Right?
 -  "Of course!"

1202
00:47:16,810 --> 00:47:19,500
Running Man visited me...

1203
00:47:19,500 --> 00:47:20,710
Did they call you a fatty again?

1204
00:47:20,710 --> 00:47:22,830
No, they didn't call me a fatty.

1205
00:47:22,830 --> 00:47:27,440
- They came over to apologise.
 -  Really?

1206
00:47:27,440 --> 00:47:28,810
They all came.

1207
00:47:28,810 --> 00:47:30,970
- Jong Kook is actually next to me.
 -  Let them talk.

1208
00:47:30,970 --> 00:47:32,970
I'll give the phone to Jong Kook, okay?

1209
00:47:32,970 --> 00:47:34,070
(He's flustered.)

1210
00:47:34,070 --> 00:47:36,270
- Hello, Mrs Moon.
 -  Hey.

1211
00:47:36,270 --> 00:47:37,320
Yes, Mrs Moon.

1212
00:47:38,220 --> 00:47:40,270
- My granddaughter...
 -  Yes?

1213
00:47:40,270 --> 00:47:43,100
keeps calling Hee Jun a fatty after she saw you say it.

1214
00:47:43,520 --> 00:47:46,970
(Her uncle is a fatty.)

1215
00:47:46,970 --> 00:47:50,120
She's my sister's daughter.

1216
00:47:50,720 --> 00:47:53,140
- Is that what she said?
 -  She's your sister's daughter.

1217
00:47:53,140 --> 00:47:56,370
I'll take charge and make Hee Jun exercise.

1218
00:47:56,370 --> 00:47:57,740
- This is good.
 -  I'll keep my promise.

1219
00:47:57,740 --> 00:47:59,870
- That sounds like a good idea.
 -  That's great.

1220
00:47:59,870 --> 00:48:01,040
- I'm being serious.
 -  That's nice of you.

